# Resume Project Description

## Project 1 (Resume Friendly)

### Linux Shell Automation Projects
- Developed multiple Bash scripting projects for Linux automation and system monitoring.
- Implemented RAM monitoring, disk usage tracking, URL status checking, and live terminal timer utilities.
- Utilized Linux tools such as awk, sed, grep, and cron for scripting and automation tasks.
- Improved understanding of Linux administration, shell scripting, and DevOps fundamentals.

